What you need to know:

4 - Lille need four more points to be certain of winning their fourth French league title.3 - Pochettino has lost three of his nine home Ligue 1 games in charge of PSG. That is as many defeats as Thomas Tuchel had in 42 home matches and as many as the previous two coaches -- Unai Emery and Laurent Blanc -- had in 95 home league games combined.17 - If Lyon avoid defeat in Nimes they will equal the French top-flight record of 17 away league games without losing in a single season, matching their own achievement from 2005/06 and that of Saint-Etienne in 1980/81.